<div class="section" id="make-it-social-ltd-edinburgh-uk">
<h2><a class="reference external" href="http://www.makeitsocial.com.com">Make It Social Ltd</a> (Edinburgh, UK)</h2>
<p><em>Posted 13-February-2013</em></p>
<p><strong>Job Description</strong>:</p>
<p>Python Developer required for Edinburgh based Social Start Up to help fulfill it's worldwide potential.</p>
<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>
<ul class="simple">
<li>Advanced Python/PHP skills</li>
<li>Passionate about coding</li>
<li>Ability to work in team environment</li>
<li>Innovative</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>About the company</strong></p>
<p>Make It Social is a brand new piece of software based in Edinburgh. Our technology solves the problems associated with arranging a group experience and has potential to grow exponentially.
After launching in November 2012, we have secured a number of key clients.
The current software is in Beta testing after being built by an Edinburgh based firm.
We are looking to bring further development in house to ensure continuity and to be able to satify our clients needs.</p>
<p>90% of work will be done on Python and 10% will be PHP.</p>
<p>This is a full time paid position based in Edinburgh. Salary between £20-40,000 depending on previous experience + Share option scheme after probationary period.</p>
<p><strong>Contact Info:</strong></p>
<ul class="simple">
<li><strong>Contact</strong>: Eddie Robb</li>
<li><strong>E-mail contact</strong>: <a class="reference external" href="mailto:eddie&#37;&#52;&#48;makeitsocial&#46;com">eddie<span>&#64;</span>makeitsocial<span>&#46;</span>com</a></li>
<li><strong>Other Contact Info</strong>: 07920016588</li>
<li><strong>Web</strong>: <a class="reference external" href="http://www.makeitsocial.com">http://www.makeitsocial.com</a></li>
<li><strong>No telecommuting</strong></li>
</ul>
</div>
