<h2><a class="reference external" href="http://www.harveynash.com/uk">Harvey Nash (Agency)</a> (London, UK)</h2>
<p><em>Posted 12-February-2013</em></p>
<p><strong>Job Description</strong>:</p>
<p>International digital agency, looking for an innovative and creative Python developer to join the team help delivering cutting-edge projects</p>
<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>
<ul class="simple">
<li>Strong knowledge of software development with 5+ years experience hand-coding Python using Django</li>
<li>Exposure to the Software Development Lifecycle in an agency environment</li>
<li>Knowledge of Design Patterns, Advanced Object-Oriented Programming, REST Web Services, Backend/External System Integration and experience with industry frameworks</li>
<li>Understanding of good design principles and ability to adhere to complex design specifications during implementation</li>
<li>Demonstrable experience in an agency creative process and comfortable working with designers</li>
<li>Knowledge of and experience working with Continuous Integration &amp; Build Management systems an advantage</li>
<li>Commercial experience with Git (and git-flow) or similar version control</li>
<li>Comfortable contributing and reviewing functional and technical documentation</li>
<li>Exposure to using techniques from the Agile methodology in an agency environment an advantage</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>About the company</strong></p>
<p>Well established and successful my Client is an independent creative digital agency with an international presence and a very strong client list. My Client has a broad outlook on Digital technologies and devices which guarantees a varied and exciting career.</p>
<p><strong>Contact Info:</strong></p>
